trans-unit.source: FastTrack Center Benefit for Azure Active Directory Premium
trans-unit.target: FastTrack Center Benefit for Azure Active Directory Premium

trans-unit.source: You can use the FastTrack Center Benefit when you purchase at least 150 licenses for Microsoft AADP in an eligible plan.
trans-unit.target: You can use the FastTrack Center Benefit when you purchase at least 150 licenses for Microsoft AADP in an eligible plan.

trans-unit.source: The FastTrack Center Benefit lets you work with Microsoft specialists to assess, remediate, and enable eligible services.
trans-unit.target: The FastTrack Center Benefit lets you work with Microsoft specialists to assess, remediate, and enable eligible services.

trans-unit.source: This article provides details about plan and service eligibility for the FastTrack Center Benefit.
trans-unit.target: This article provides details about plan and service eligibility for the FastTrack Center Benefit.

trans-unit.source: To learn about the Onboarding process as well as roles and responsibilities, see <link><linkText>FastTrack Center Benefit Process for Azure Active Directory Premium </linkText><title></title></link>.
trans-unit.target: To learn about the Onboarding process as well as roles and responsibilities, see <link><linkText>FastTrack Center Benefit Process for Azure Active Directory Premium </linkText><title></title></link>.

trans-unit.source: Eligible services
trans-unit.target: Eligible services

trans-unit.source: If you purchase any of the following Microsoft online services through an eligible plan, Microsoft will help you onboard to them.
trans-unit.target: If you purchase any of the following Microsoft online services through an eligible plan, Microsoft will help you onboard to them.

trans-unit.source: Microsoft will attempt to contact you within 30 days from the date you purchase an eligible plan.
trans-unit.target: Microsoft will attempt to contact you within 30 days from the date you purchase an eligible plan.

trans-unit.source: You can also request assistance from the <link><linkText>FastTrack Center</linkText><title></title></link> if you are ready to deploy these services for your organization.
trans-unit.target: You can also request assistance from the <link><linkText>FastTrack Center</linkText><title></title></link> if you are ready to deploy these services for your organization.

trans-unit.source: To request assistance, sign in to the FastTrack Center (http://fasttrack.microsoft.com), go to the dashboard, select your company name, click the Offers tab, and click the request assistance button for the eligible service.
trans-unit.target: To request assistance, sign in to the FastTrack Center (http://fasttrack.microsoft.com), go to the dashboard, select your company name, click the Offers tab, and click the request assistance button for the eligible service.

trans-unit.source: Customers can opt-in to the FastTrack Center Benefit once per each eligible Microsoft online service within the 12-month period after initial contact.
trans-unit.target: Customers can opt-in to the FastTrack Center Benefit once per each eligible Microsoft online service within the 12-month period after initial contact.
